[No. 6,418. In Bank.] CHARLES SHIMMINS v. THE FIFTEENTH DISTRICT COURT FOR THE CITY AND COUNTY OF SAN FRANCISCO. Certiorari. Application for the writ of certiorari to the Fifteenth District Court. Dwinelle, J.

S. M. Wilson, for Plaintiff.

B. S. Brooks, for Defendant.

The Court:

Upon the authority of Goodale v. The Fifteenth District Court, 56 Cal. 26, writ dismissed.

[Justice McKinstry disqualified, Justice McKee not sitting, Justice Sharpstein dissenting.]
